---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE_AUTHOR } from '../consts';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
    <article class="prose max-w-none">
      <h1>About</h1>
      <p>
          Hi, I'm {SITE_AUTHOR}. This is my personal blog, where I write about
          programming - with particular focus on Idris, Java, JVM.
      </p>
      <p>
        Much of my work centers on running functional languages on the JVM,
        including the Idris JVM backend, which compiles Idris to JVM bytecode.
        Here I share notes, experiments, and write-ups from those projects, plus
        whatever else I happen to be exploring along the way.
      </p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>You can find me and my projects on GitHub:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/mmhelloworld">GitHub</a></li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
